11:52.212 --> 11:53.588
Daddy rules the roost.

11:53.630 --> 11:55.965
Oh, hi, Kitty.

11:57.509 --> 11:59.760
I got you!

11:57.509 --> 11:59.760
(laughing)

11:59.802 --> 12:02.055
(both laughing)

11:59.802 --> 12:02.055
I did.

12:02.096 --> 12:03.223
To being whipped.

12:03.264 --> 12:04.391
Like butter, my friend.

12:04.432 --> 12:06.560
(Reese grunts viciously)

12:06.601 --> 12:09.312
Kitty.

12:14.817 --> 12:16.486
Where are those guys?

12:16.528 --> 12:19.573
Hal probably dragged

12:16.528 --> 12:19.573
Abe over to the bar.

12:19.614 --> 12:20.948
You know, if he's drunk,

12:19.614 --> 12:20.948
so help me...

