12:40.134 --> 12:41.802
Excuse me?

12:40.134 --> 12:41.802
No-no-no,

12:41.844 --> 12:42.596
it's fine.

12:42.637 --> 12:43.804
Something wrong?

12:43.846 --> 12:45.265
