I don't think so.

12:49.477 --> 12:50.811
Instead of arguing with me,

12:49.477 --> 12:50.811
why don't you

12:50.853 --> 12:52.272
just march back

12:50.853 --> 12:52.272
to the kitchen and make...

12:52.313 --> 12:54.482
No-no-no.

12:52.313 --> 12:54.482
I like cranberry juice.

12:54.524 --> 12:56.943
Very healthy for you. Mmm...

13:01.030 --> 13:02.823
MALCOLM:

13:01.030 --> 13:02.823
Hey, Reese, that's enough!

13:02.865 --> 13:04.409
This isn't funny anymore.

13:04.451 --> 13:05.826
Okay, okay.

13:05.868 --> 13:07.454
Man, look what

13:05.868 --> 13:07.454
your shoulders did

13:07.495 --> 13:08.663
to my knuckles.

13:12.333 --> 13:15.836
I'll get you

13:12.333 --> 13:15.836
when I come back.

13:15.878 --> 13:18.839
I even knew...

13:18.881 --> 13:20.841
he was going...

13:20.883 --> 13:22.260
to do that.

13:22.302 --> 13:24.429
She won't let me

13:24.471 --> 13:27.474
have butter on my

13:24.471 --> 13:27.474
bread--  butter.

13:27.515 --> 13:30.685
I haven't eaten the

13:27.515 --> 13:30.685
stuff in ten years.

13:30.727 --> 13:33.854
How'd this happen?

13:33.896 --> 13:35.774
We weren't always this way.

13:35.814 --> 13:36.857
Actually, I was.

13:36.899 --> 13:38.025
Classic story--

13:38.067 --> 13:41.738
raised by a grandmother

13:38.067 --> 13:41.738
and four spinster aunts.

13:41.780 --> 13:44.865
I used to wash their

13:41.780 --> 13:44.865
hair on Saturday nights.

13:44.907 --> 13:47.868
You poor bastard,

13:44.907 --> 13:47.868
you never had a chance.

13:47.910 --> 13:51.830
Damn it... enough is enough!

14:04.969 --> 14:06.721
(gasps)

14:06.763 --> 14:08.640
You go, Abe!

14:11.518 --> 14:13.520
Go! Go! Go!

14:23.446 --> 14:24.905
Sir?

14:24.947 --> 14:26.324
SPANGLER:

14:24.947 --> 14:26.324
Go away!

14:26.366 --> 14:28.576
I told you I did not

14:26.366 --> 14:28.576
want to be disturbed.

14:28.618 --> 14:31.162
My aunt and I are...

14:28.618 --> 14:31.162
catching up.

14:31.204 --> 14:35.041
I... I thought you said

14:31.204 --> 14:35.041
it was your mother, sir.

14:36.543 --> 14:37.918
Go away!

14:37.960 --> 14:39.212
I wish I could, sir,

14:39.253 --> 14:41.088
but we have

14:39.253 --> 14:41.088
a bit of a situation.

14:41.130 --> 14:43.132
See, we decided

14:41.130 --> 14:43.132
to have this party

14:43.174 --> 14:44.634
and it kind of

14:43.174 --> 14:44.634
got out of hand...

14:44.676 --> 14:45.926
I don't care, cadet.

14:45.968 --> 14:47.928
I will deal with

14:45.968 --> 14:47.928
it in the morning.

14:45.968 --> 14:47.928
Yeah, but...

14:47.970 --> 14:49.222
In the morning!

14:49.263 --> 14:51.932
It's just that we invited

14:49.263 --> 14:51.932
some of the local girls...

14:51.974 --> 14:53.059
Local girls?!

14:55.812 --> 14:57.980
There are local girls

14:55.812 --> 14:57.980
inside the perimeter?

14:58.022 --> 14:59.357
Have they killed anyone?

14:59.399 --> 15:00.608
N-No, sir,

15:00.650 --> 15:02.777
but I saw one of them

15:00.650 --> 15:02.777
eat a raw chicken whole.

15:02.819 --> 15:06.406
WOMAN: Spangy.

15:02.819 --> 15:06.406
Uh... just a minute... Mother.

15:06.447 --> 15:08.867
Do you have any idea

15:06.447 --> 15:08.867
what you have done?

15:08.908 --> 15:11.118
Marlin Academy

15:08.908 --> 15:11.118
cannot exist

15:11.160 --> 15:13.954
without the support, the

15:11.160 --> 15:13.954
goodwill and cooperation

15:13.996 --> 15:15.415
of the local community.

15:15.456 --> 15:16.957
The police chief and the mayor

15:16.999 --> 15:18.585
both sit

15:16.999 --> 15:18.585
on our board of governors!

15:18.626 --> 15:20.461
The fire chief

15:18.626 --> 15:20.461
is a regent!

15:20.503 --> 15:24.215
And right now their psychotic

15:20.503 --> 15:24.215
offspring are in there

15:24.257 --> 15:26.843
tearing up the floorboards!

15:26.885 --> 15:29.970
It won't be long

15:26.885 --> 15:29.970
before they're in the air ducts.

15:30.012 --> 15:31.972
What are we going

15:30.012 --> 15:31.972
to do, sir?

15:32.014 --> 15:35.226
We are going to do

15:32.014 --> 15:35.226
what any self-respecting

15:32.014 --> 15:35.226
member of society does

15:35.268 --> 15:38.062
in a situation like this--

15:35.268 --> 15:38.062
we're going to keep it quiet.

15:38.104 --> 15:39.564
But they're destroying

15:38.104 --> 15:39.564
the school.

15:39.606 --> 15:41.608
Let's hope that's

15:39.606 --> 15:41.608
all they do, cadet.

15:41.649 --> 15:43.651
I'm afraid this is

15:41.649 --> 15:43.651
like an oil fire--

15:43.693 --> 15:45.570
we have to let it

15:43.693 --> 15:45.570
burn itself out.

15:45.612 --> 15:48.740
Oh, yeah, I forgot--

15:45.612 --> 15:48.740
one of them started an oil fire.

15:52.702 --> 15:55.705
So...

15:55.747 --> 15:57.998
did you see

15:55.747 --> 15:57.998
any good movies lately?

15:58.040 --> 16:00.209
Well, we just saw

15:58.040 --> 16:00.209
Les Amants du Pont-Neuf.

16:00.251 --> 16:01.377
Did you see it?

16:01.419 --> 16:03.296
No.

16:04.881 --> 16:06.173
Last movie I saw was

16:06.215 --> 16:09.009
The Computer Wore Tennis Shoes

16:06.215 --> 16:09.009
on cable.

16:09.051 --> 16:11.679
Oh, my God! Kurt Russell!

16:09.051 --> 16:11.679
Yes.

16:11.721 --> 16:14.014
Oh, I had such a crush on him

16:11.721 --> 16:14.014
in those Disney films.

16:14.056 --> 16:17.017
I did, too--

16:14.056 --> 16:17.017
especially in  Now You See It...

16:17.059 --> 16:18.227
BOTH:

16:17.059 --> 16:18.227
Now You Don't!

16:18.269 --> 16:20.020
Oh, God...

16:18.269 --> 16:20.020
Oh, he was so cute.

16:20.062 --> 16:22.857
Did you see  The Strongest Man

16:20.062 --> 16:22.857
in the World?

16:20.062 --> 16:22.857
About 50 times.

16:22.899 --> 16:26.611
Oh, my God!

16:22.899 --> 16:26.611
I just wanted to reach out

16:22.899 --> 16:26.611
and grab that tush.

16:26.653 --> 16:28.404
I am so terrible.

16:28.446 --> 16:30.072
(both laughing)

16:30.114 --> 16:32.116
Seriously, this

16:30.114 --> 16:32.116
has got to stop.

16:32.158 --> 16:34.285
I'm actually starting

16:32.158 --> 16:34.285
to feel bad

16:34.327 --> 16:37.497
and plus... I'm

16:34.327 --> 16:37.497
kind of getting

16:34.327 --> 16:37.497
bored creatively.

16:38.498 --> 16:39.874
Oh, my God!

16:39.916 --> 16:41.334
Is that a snake?

16:39.916 --> 16:41.334
Stevie, don't.

16:41.375 --> 16:43.127
REESE:

16:41.375 --> 16:43.127
Sucker.

16:44.545 --> 16:46.422
Snake...

16:46.464 --> 16:48.007
I'm an idiot.

16:54.013 --> 16:55.682
(Lois and Kitty laughing)

16:58.476 --> 17:00.060
Oh...

17:00.102 --> 17:02.229
I'm so glad we decided

17:00.102 --> 17:02.229
to have this dinner.

17:02.271 --> 17:05.065
So am I.

17:02.271 --> 17:05.065
I feel so much better now.

17:05.107 --> 17:06.776
Better?

17:06.818 --> 17:08.277
About you and your family.

17:08.319 --> 17:09.904
What?

17:09.946 --> 17:11.155
A-A-About Malcolm and Stevie

17:11.197 --> 17:13.157
because they spend

17:11.197 --> 17:13.157
so much time together,

17:13.199 --> 17:15.368
and now that we've gotten

17:13.199 --> 17:15.368
to know each other,

17:15.409 --> 17:16.452
I just feel better.

17:16.494 --> 17:18.162
Wait a minute.

17:18.204 --> 17:20.373
You mean this wasn't about

17:18.204 --> 17:20.373
you wanting to be friends?

17:20.414 --> 17:21.541
Yes, it was.

17:21.582 --> 17:23.167
No, it wasn't.

17:23.209 --> 17:24.585
You were checking us out.

17:24.627 --> 17:27.254
You wanted to see if we were

17:24.627 --> 17:27.254
good enough for your family.

17:27.296 --> 17:29.298
No, no, no. I-I wouldn't

17:27.296 --> 17:29.298
put it that way.

17:29.340 --> 17:32.301
I would, because

17:29.340 --> 17:32.301
that's what you're doing.

17:32.343 --> 17:34.136
How dare you!

17:34.178 --> 17:35.513
You can't judge us.

17:35.555 --> 17:36.681
You know,

17:36.723 --> 17:38.516
you are not

17:36.723 --> 17:38.516
so perfect yourself, lady.

17:38.558 --> 17:41.185
Hell, you are one of the most

17:38.558 --> 17:41.185
uptight, repressed people

17:41.227 --> 17:42.520
I've ever met in my life.

17:42.562 --> 17:46.106
Did you know that Kurt Russell

17:42.562 --> 17:46.106
was the jungle boy

17:46.148 --> 17:48.108
on  Gilligan's Island?

17:48.150 --> 17:49.402
Don't change the subject.

17:49.443 --> 17:50.486
We're having an

17:49.443 --> 17:50.486
argument here.

17:50.528 --> 17:51.571
I yell at you;

17:50.528 --> 17:51.571
you yell at me--

17:51.612 --> 17:52.530
that's what you do.

17:52.572 --> 17:53.614
What's wrong with you?

17:53.656 --> 17:55.115
Whatever you say

17:53.656 --> 17:55.115
is wrong with me

17:55.157 --> 17:56.283
is what's wrong with me.

17:56.325 --> 17:57.410
There-- problem solved.

17:57.451 --> 17:59.078
(chuckles nervously)

18:09.338 --> 18:11.340
(groans softly)

18:13.760 --> 18:17.221
Okay, that's just freaky.

18:17.263 --> 18:19.515
REESE:

18:17.263 --> 18:19.515
Hey, I'm getting

18:17.263 --> 18:19.515
good with my left.

18:19.557 --> 18:20.808
Thanks, Stevie.

18:21.976 --> 18:24.729
I... give up.

18:24.771 --> 18:26.146
I'm going to...

18:26.188 --> 18:28.148
the car.

18:34.447 --> 18:36.156
(crying softly)

18:36.198 --> 18:37.366
Way to go, Reese.

18:37.408 --> 18:39.118
Aw, geez!

18:47.627 --> 18:50.254
Crying on... command...

18:50.296 --> 18:53.173
got me... a cable modem.

18:54.592 --> 18:55.551
You have a real problem.

18:55.593 --> 18:56.677
Have you never

18:55.593 --> 18:56.677
yelled at anyone

18:56.719 --> 18:57.971
in your entire life?

18:58.012 --> 18:59.555
I just don't see

18:58.012 --> 18:59.555
what it accomplishes.

18:59.597 --> 19:00.765
Are you kidding?

19:00.807 --> 19:02.558
Most of the time,

19:00.807 --> 19:02.558
if you're not yelling,

19:02.600 --> 19:03.893
they're not listening.

19:03.935 --> 19:06.479
Lois, our situation

19:03.935 --> 19:06.479
is difficult enough

19:06.520 --> 19:10.566
without me adding

19:06.520 --> 19:10.566
a bunch of negativity to it.

19:10.608 --> 19:13.193
What situation? You mean Stevie?

19:13.235 --> 19:15.488
He's fine!

19:13.235 --> 19:15.488
He's not going to wither away

19:15.529 --> 19:18.407
because you blow off steam

19:15.529 --> 19:18.407
every once in a while.

19:20.242 --> 19:22.286
Hey, why don't you give

19:20.242 --> 19:22.286
both of you a break?

19:25.247 --> 19:26.373
Go ahead, hit me.

19:26.415 --> 19:27.875
Get it over with.

19:32.922 --> 19:34.799
Ow... ow...

19:34.841 --> 19:37.677
Let me... help you.

19:39.261 --> 19:41.514
Reap...

19:41.555 --> 19:43.182
the whirlwind!

19:44.266 --> 19:45.601
(grunting)

19:45.643 --> 19:49.229
Finally-- justice.

19:49.271 --> 19:51.732
I mean, if he doesn't kill him.

19:51.774 --> 19:52.984
(grunting)

19:55.486 --> 19:58.238
Stevie, what the hell

19:55.486 --> 19:58.238
do you think you're doing?!

19:58.280 --> 19:59.657
You are in so

19:58.280 --> 19:59.657
much trouble!

19:59.699 --> 20:01.492
This behavior is

19:59.699 --> 20:01.492
totally unacceptable.

20:01.534 --> 20:04.162
We are at a restaurant--

20:01.534 --> 20:04.162
what is wrong with you?

20:05.287 --> 20:06.706
Don't you take that tone

20:05.287 --> 20:06.706
with me!

20:06.747 --> 20:08.332
You just wait

20:06.747 --> 20:08.332
till we get home!

20:08.374 --> 20:09.876
He bruised the bone.

20:09.917 --> 20:11.251
Oh, like you

20:09.917 --> 20:11.251
didn't deserve it.

20:11.293 --> 20:12.879
Good for you! I knew

20:11.293 --> 20:12.879
you had it in you.

20:12.920 --> 20:14.254
Shut your trap!

20:14.296 --> 20:16.549
Excuse me, would

20:14.296 --> 20:16.549
you mind please

20:14.296 --> 20:16.549
keeping it down?

20:16.590 --> 20:18.134
Would you mind

20:16.590 --> 20:18.134
going to hell?

20:18.176 --> 20:19.886
And I absolutely did order tea!

20:19.927 --> 20:23.263
How hard is it to remember

20:19.927 --> 20:23.263
