20:23.305 --> 20:24.849
Kitty, there's going to be

20:23.305 --> 20:24.849
some changes...

20:24.891 --> 20:27.267
And you-- Mr. Ho Hos

20:24.891 --> 20:27.267
in his sock drawer!

20:27.309 --> 20:28.686
Who do you think

20:27.309 --> 20:28.686
you're kidding?

20:28.728 --> 20:30.312
Honey, you have

20:28.728 --> 20:30.312
to pace yourself.

20:30.354 --> 20:32.190
And another thing,

20:30.354 --> 20:32.190
Don Juan,

20:32.272 --> 20:34.108
there are two people

20:32.272 --> 20:34.108
in that bed!

20:35.401 --> 20:37.904
You know, I really don't

20:35.401 --> 20:37.904
feel very good.

20:39.530 --> 20:41.323
And I had it with your poker

20:39.530 --> 20:41.323
nights and your idiot frien...

20:47.329 --> 20:50.791
I think this is

20:47.329 --> 20:50.791
