I'd say we got off lucky.

20:53.335 --> 20:55.295
This happened once

20:53.335 --> 20:55.295
before in '72--

20:55.337 --> 20:59.258
we had to bulldoze

20:55.337 --> 20:59.258
the amphitheater.

21:03.262 --> 21:05.305
It's Horton.

21:05.347 --> 21:07.307
Hey, Horton, you okay?

21:07.349 --> 21:09.518
What happened?

21:09.560 --> 21:14.148
I've seen things, Francis...

21:14.190 --> 21:17.568
terrible things...

21:17.610 --> 21:20.238
and I... I think I'm engaged.

21:23.365 --> 21:25.118
Come on, children,

21:23.365 --> 21:25.118
quickly, quickly.

21:23.365 --> 21:25.118
KITTY: Those pants went

21:25.159 --> 21:26.827
out of style in the '80s

21:25.159 --> 21:26.827
