21:26.869 --> 21:28.204
Don't you give me that look.

21:28.246 --> 21:29.329
You got a eye problem?

21:29.371 --> 21:30.998
Whoa. Interesting dinner.

21:31.040 --> 21:33.000
Stevie beat the crap

21:31.040 --> 21:33.000
out of Reese,

21:33.042 --> 21:34.334
his dad got drunk,

21:34.376 --> 21:37.337
and his mom's gone

21:34.376 --> 21:37.337
totally psycho.

21:37.379 --> 21:39.339
Oh, my God... we're contagious.

